---
const uid = Math.random().toString(36).slice(2, 8);
const arrowId = `arrow-${uid}`;
---

<figure class="mx-auto max-w-2xl my-10">
  <svg
    width="680"
    height="628"
    viewBox="0 0 680 628"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    class="w-full h-auto"
    role="img"
    aria-labelledby={`doctrinal-stack-title-${uid}`}
    aria-describedby={`doctrinal-stack-desc-${uid}`}
    style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"
  >
    <title id={`doctrinal-stack-title-${uid}`}>South Africa's doctrinal stack</title>
    <desc id={`doctrinal-stack-desc-${uid}`}>
      A five-tier diagram of the documents from which South Africa's grand strategy must be
      reconstructed. From top to bottom: Constitutional tier (Constitution of South Africa, Section
      198, 1996); Strategic tier (National Security Strategy, National Intelligence Estimate, and
      National Intelligence Priorities, 2024 to 2029); Foreign-policy tier (White Paper on the
      Diplomacy of Ubuntu 2011, the 2022 Framework Document on the National Interest, and the DIRCO
      Strategic Plan 2025 to 2030); Defence tier (1996 White Paper on Defence, 2015 Defence Review,
      and the pending Long-Term Force Evolution Strategy 2025 to 2055); Development tier (National
      Development Plan, Vision 2030, adopted 2012). Each tier binds on the tiers below it, so
      authority flows downward through the stack.
    </desc>

    <defs>
      <marker
        id={arrowId}
        viewBox="0 0 10 10"
        refX="9"
        refY="5"
        markerWidth="8"
        markerHeight="8"
        orient="auto"
      >
        <path d="M1 1L9 5L1 9" fill="none" stroke="#888780" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </marker>
    </defs>

    <!-- Figure heading -->
    <text x="340" y="24" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13" font-weight="600" fill="#264A2C" letter-spacing="1.2">
      SOUTH AFRICA&apos;S DOCTRINAL STACK
    </text>
    <text x="340" y="46" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12" fill="#4A4A4A" font-style="italic">
      Five tiers of grand-strategic doctrine — each layer binding on the layers below
    </text>

    <!-- Tier 1: Constitutional -->
    <rect x="70" y="78" width="540" height="66" rx="6" fill="#264A2C"/>
    <text x="92" y="104" font-size="11" font-weight="600" fill="#C6D4C9" letter-spacing="1.4">
      I &middot; CONSTITUTIONAL TIER
    </text>
    <text x="92" y="128" font-size="14" font-weight="500" fill="#FFFFFF">
      Constitution of South Africa &mdash; Section 198
    </text>
    <text x="588" y="128" text-anchor="end" font-size="13" fill="#C6D4C9" font-variant-numeric="tabular-nums">
      1996
    </text>

    <!-- Binding arrow 1→2 -->
    <line x1="340" y1="148" x2="340" y2="162" stroke="#888780" stroke-width="1" marker-end={`url(#${arrowId})`}/>

    <!-- Tier 2: Strategic -->
    <rect x="70" y="166" width="540" height="66" rx="6" fill="#355E3B"/>
    <text x="92" y="192" font-size="11" font-weight="600" fill="#D6E2D8" letter-spacing="1.4">
      II &middot; STRATEGIC TIER
    </text>
    <text x="92" y="216" font-size="14" font-weight="500" fill="#FFFFFF">
      National Security Strategy &middot; NIE &middot; Intelligence Priorities
    </text>
    <text x="588" y="216" text-anchor="end" font-size="13" fill="#D6E2D8" font-variant-numeric="tabular-nums">
      2024&ndash;29
    </text>

    <!-- Binding arrow 2→3 -->
    <line x1="340" y1="236" x2="340" y2="250" stroke="#888780" stroke-width="1" marker-end={`url(#${arrowId})`}/>

    <!-- Tier 3: Foreign-policy -->
    <rect x="70" y="254" width="540" height="100" rx="6" fill="#4D7B54"/>
    <text x="92" y="280" font-size="11" font-weight="600" fill="#E4ECE5" letter-spacing="1.4">
      III &middot; FOREIGN-POLICY TIER
    </text>
    <text x="92" y="302" font-size="14" font-weight="500" fill="#FFFFFF">
      Diplomacy of Ubuntu
    </text>
    <text x="588" y="302" text-anchor="end" font-size="13" fill="#E4ECE5" font-variant-numeric="tabular-nums">
      2011
    </text>
    <text x="92" y="322" font-size="14" font-weight="500" fill="#FFFFFF">
      Framework Document on the National Interest
    </text>
    <text x="588" y="322" text-anchor="end" font-size="13" fill="#E4ECE5" font-variant-numeric="tabular-nums">
      2022
    </text>
    <text x="92" y="342" font-size="14" font-weight="500" fill="#FFFFFF">
      DIRCO Strategic Plan
    </text>
    <text x="588" y="342" text-anchor="end" font-size="13" fill="#E4ECE5" font-variant-numeric="tabular-nums">
      2025&ndash;30
    </text>

    <!-- Binding arrow 3→4 -->
    <line x1="340" y1="358" x2="340" y2="372" stroke="#888780" stroke-width="1" marker-end={`url(#${arrowId})`}/>

    <!-- Tier 4: Defence -->
    <rect x="70" y="376" width="540" height="100" rx="6" fill="#88A68F"/>
    <text x="92" y="402" font-size="11" font-weight="600" fill="#2F4A34" letter-spacing="1.4">
      IV &middot; DEFENCE TIER
    </text>
    <text x="92" y="424" font-size="14" font-weight="500" fill="#1A1A1A">
      White Paper on Defence
    </text>
    <text x="588" y="424" text-anchor="end" font-size="13" fill="#2F4A34" font-variant-numeric="tabular-nums">
      1996
    </text>
    <text x="92" y="444" font-size="14" font-weight="500" fill="#1A1A1A">
      Defence Review
    </text>
    <text x="588" y="444" text-anchor="end" font-size="13" fill="#2F4A34" font-variant-numeric="tabular-nums">
      2015
    </text>
    <text x="92" y="464" font-size="14" font-weight="500" fill="#1A1A1A">
      Long-Term Force Evolution Strategy (pending)
    </text>
    <text x="588" y="464" text-anchor="end" font-size="13" fill="#2F4A34" font-variant-numeric="tabular-nums">
      2025&ndash;55
    </text>

    <!-- Binding arrow 4→5 -->
    <line x1="340" y1="480" x2="340" y2="494" stroke="#888780" stroke-width="1" marker-end={`url(#${arrowId})`}/>

    <!-- Tier 5: Development -->
    <rect x="70" y="498" width="540" height="66" rx="6" fill="#C2D3C6"/>
    <text x="92" y="524" font-size="11" font-weight="600" fill="#264A2C" letter-spacing="1.4">
      V &middot; DEVELOPMENT TIER
    </text>
    <text x="92" y="548" font-size="14" font-weight="500" fill="#1A1A1A">
      National Development Plan &mdash; Vision 2030
    </text>
    <text x="588" y="548" text-anchor="end" font-size="13" fill="#264A2C" font-variant-numeric="tabular-nums">
      2012
    </text>

    <!-- Caption -->
    <text x="340" y="592" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12" fill="#5F5E5A">
      Binding authority flows downward. Each tier inherits the normative constraints of every tier above it.
    </text>
    <text x="340" y="610" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12" fill="#5F5E5A" font-style="italic">
      Vertical tension between tiers is where grand strategy is negotiated.
    </text>
  </svg>
  <figcaption class="sr-only">
    Figure: South Africa&rsquo;s doctrinal stack — the five tiers of documents from which the
    country&rsquo;s grand strategy must be reconstructed, with binding authority flowing downward
    from the Constitution to the National Development Plan.
  </figcaption>
</figure>
